About Isobel Mitton

Isobel Mitton is a scifi/fantasy author of the “Across the Realm” scifi/fantasy book series. She also writes Erotic romance based on the Hip Hop world as Madeleine Mitton.

Isobel is Canadian and African. She is also a certified witchdoctor/traditional healer with clairvoyance gifts.

SUBSCRIBE

To this channel for psychic readings, Initiation classes from her tribe, the Zezuru, stories of Africa, and updates on her books.

Initiation classes – From the Zezuru tribe in Southern Africa.
Be the one – HIV awareness
Stories from an African village – Isobel shares stories of growing up while straddling urban Africa and rural Africa.
The Books – Isobel talks about her books, scifi/fantasy and erotic romance.

WHAT IS ZINATHA?


ZINATHA is an association of registered and licenced traditional healers comprising of spirit mediums, herbalists, faith healers & midwives.
